name: Miss K8
description: '''Kateryna Kremko''' ({{langx|uk|Катерина Кремко}}), known professionally as '''Miss K8''' (born 18 June 1981), is a [[Disc jockey|DJ]] from [[Kyiv]], Ukraine. She has played at music festivals such as [[Defqon.1 Festival|Defqon.1]] and [[Masters of Hardcore]], gaining recognition for her performances. In 2019, Kateryna took some time off due to pregnancy.
